flowchart TD
    E2E[E2E — Physical device smoke tests<br/>~5 tests · critical path only]
    UI[UI Tests — Espresso / XCUITest / Maestro<br/>~50 tests · key user journeys]
    INT[Integration — Robolectric + DB + API mock<br/>~100 tests · cross-layer contracts]
    SNAP[Snapshot — Paparazzi / iOS Snapshot<br/>~1,000 tests · every component variant]
    UNIT[Unit — JUnit5 + Turbine / Swift Testing<br/>~10,000 tests · ViewModel / UseCase / Repository]

    UNIT --> SNAP
    SNAP --> INT
    INT --> UI
    UI --> E2E

    UNIT -.runs on.-> JVM[JVM — milliseconds per test]
    SNAP -.runs on.-> JVM
    INT -.runs on.-> JVM
    UI -.runs on.-> EMU[Emulator / Simulator]
    E2E -.runs on.-> LAB[Firebase Test Lab — physical devices]

    PACT[Pact Contracts] -.guards.-> INT

